<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All I know is that they're best friends,</b></font>

150
00:12:47,344 --> 00:12:51,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and from the beginning,
they were always analyzing</b></font>

151
00:12:51,184 --> 00:12:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and developing their technique together.</b></font>

152
00:13:00,854 --> 00:13:05,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Isn't she like a rally navigator?</b></font>

153
00:13:05,194 --> 00:13:09,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--That makes it worse for Takumi.
--Yeah.</b></font>

154
00:13:09,834 --> 00:13:13,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No way! He won't lose!</b></font>

155
00:13:13,064 --> 00:13:16,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But with a good navigator,</b></font>

156
00:13:16,334 --> 00:13:20,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako can concentrate fully on driving.</b></font>

157
00:13:22,844 --> 00:13:24,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Obstacle ahead!</b></font>

158
00:13:24,684 --> 00:13:27,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Avoid it and cut inside!
--Yeah.</b></font>

159
00:14:23,304 --> 00:14:27,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He keeps up with our fast pace...</i></b></font>

160
00:14:27,244 --> 00:14:29,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...as if Mako's best isn't fast enough.</i></b></font>

161
00:14:29,814 --> 00:14:31,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's good!</i></b></font>

162
00:14:31,714 --> 00:14:34,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Mako, C-121 is coming up.</b></font>

163
00:14:34,984 --> 00:14:36,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll shake him off there!</b></font>

164
00:14:37,824 --> 00:14:40,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll drift from the very beginning.</b></font>

165
00:14:40,954 --> 00:14:43,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's show him what we're made of</b></font>

166
00:14:43,294 --> 00:14:46,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>at Usui's most difficult turn.</b></font>

167
00:14:46,464 --> 00:14:48,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Got it. That's right!</b></font>

168
00:14:48,494 --> 00:14:52,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll show him how drifting should be done!</b></font>

169
00:14:52,764 --> 00:14:57,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No one else has ever
cleared the turn at full speed.</b></font>

170
00:15:20,524 --> 00:15:23,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are Mako and Sayuki here tonight?</b></font>

171
00:15:23,194 --> 00:15:26,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I haven't seen them yet.</b></font>

172
00:15:26,934 --> 00:15:30,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wanna see the Sileighty's drift.</b></font>

173
00:15:30,034 --> 00:15:33,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Here at C-121 is the best place for it.</b></font>

174
00:15:33,874 --> 00:15:35,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>'Cuz it's really hard.</b></font>

175
00:15:35,974 --> 00:15:38,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the hardest.</b></font>

176
00:15:38,144 --> 00:15:41,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're considered an advanced racer here</b></font>

177
00:15:41,484 --> 00:15:44,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>if you can drift through this turn.</b></font>

178
00:15:44,154 --> 00:15:47,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Advanced in Usui means the best anywhere.</b></font>

179
00:15:47,324 --> 00:15:51,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah.
--If you don't have the
courage to come in fast,</b></font>

180
00:15:51,624 --> 00:15:55,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you won't have enough
speed to drift to the end.</b></font>

181
00:15:55,834 --> 00:15:59,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All the first-timers mess it up.</b></font>

182
00:15:59,864 --> 00:16:02,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But some can actually do it, right?</b></font>

183
00:16:02,174 --> 00:16:03,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A few.</b></font>

184
00:16:03,834 --> 00:16:08,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But only Mako's Sileighty
does it at full speed.</b></font>

185
00:16:08,374 --> 00:16:10,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know how fast she goes,</b></font>

186
00:16:10,544 --> 00:16:13,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but no one else has managed it yet.</b></font>

187
00:16:20,684 --> 00:16:23,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Someone is coming down.</b></font>

188
00:16:23,024 --> 00:16:25,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hear that squealing? They're coming in fast!</b></font>

189
00:16:28,994 --> 00:16:30,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There!</b></font>

190
00:16:30,834 --> 00:16:33,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--The Sileighty!
--It's Mako and Sayuki!</b></font>

191
00:16:33,664 --> 00:16:35,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's following them?</b></font>

192
00:16:35,834 --> 00:16:37,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are they racing?!</b></font>

193
00:16:40,604 --> 00:16:42,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six?!</b></font>

194
00:16:56,924 --> 00:16:58,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No cars ahead!</b></font>

195
00:16:58,424 --> 00:16:59,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Make it flashy, Mako!</b></font>

196
00:16:59,964 --> 00:17:02,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Yeah!
--Go!</b></font>

197
00:17:10,234 --> 00:17:12,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They're in the turn!</b></font>

198
00:17:25,984 --> 00:17:30,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That fool came into the turn
at the same speed as Mako!</b></font>

199
00:17:30,294 --> 00:17:33,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Doesn't he know how difficult C-121 is?!</b></font>

200
00:17:33,424 --> 00:17:37,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Courage alone won't let him clear the corner!</b></font>

201
00:17:44,104 --> 00:17:48,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He has guts, following Mako into this corner.</i></b></font>

202
00:17:48,344 --> 00:17:52,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But at this speed, there's no turning back.</i></b></font>

203
00:17:52,984 --> 00:17:57,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>C-121's exit narrows severely.</i></b></font>

204
00:17:57,984 --> 00:18:03,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>There is only one ideal line to the exit,</i>
<i>though there seem to be others.</i></b></font>

205
00:18:03,154 --> 00:18:07,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can you find it, your first time on this course?</b></font>

206
00:18:38,324 --> 00:18:40,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He couldn't have!</b></font>

207
00:18:43,134 --> 00:18:45,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--He cleared it.
--Unbelievable.</b></font>

208
00:18:45,704 --> 00:18:48,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who's that Eight-Six?</b></font>

209
00:18:48,004 --> 00:18:53,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could he be... the famous
Eight-Six of Mount Akina?</b></font>

210
00:18:53,004 --> 00:18:55,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have goose bumps!</b></font>

211
00:18:59,684 --> 00:19:00,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What just happened?</i></b></font>

212
00:19:00,844 --> 00:19:03,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Four-wheel drift at full speed</i></b></font>

213
00:19:03,484 --> 00:19:05,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>is ranked as "Ultra D" difficulty.</i></b></font>

214
00:19:05,984 --> 00:19:10,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even Mako missed the</i>
<i>ideal line by three inches.</i></b></font>

215
00:19:10,494 --> 00:19:15,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But he was right on it.</i></b></font>

216
00:19:24,034 --> 00:19:29,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We can't win. We chose a</i>
<i>monster as our opponent.</i></b></font>

217
00:19:44,794 --> 00:19:48,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No! You can't swing that much here!</b></font>

218
00:19:48,734 --> 00:19:52,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You couldn't have told me that sooner?</b></font>

219
00:19:52,304 --> 00:19:56,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What's wrong? Focus! This isn't like you!</b></font>

220
00:19:56,904 --> 00:19:59,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Can't you tell, Mako?</b></font>

221
00:19:59,204 --> 00:20:02,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Eight-Six is unreal.</b></font>

222
00:20:02,244 --> 00:20:06,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's way out of our league.</b></font>

223
00:20:06,314 --> 00:20:09,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What happened to your usual stubbornness?</b></font>

224
00:20:09,254 --> 00:20:12,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not even over and you're giving up?</b></font>

225
00:20:12,884 --> 00:20:15,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not me!</b></font>

226
00:20:15,094 --> 00:20:17,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess I am...</b></font>

227
00:20:17,754 --> 00:20:21,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine! I didn't know you were a quitter.</b></font>

228
00:20:21,994 --> 00:20:24,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll do it myself!</b></font>

229
00:20:31,134 --> 00:20:34,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We already knew how great he was.</b></font>

230
00:20:34,974 --> 00:20:38,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But since this is my last race...</b></font>

231
00:20:39,814 --> 00:20:43,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...we can't quit without giving it our best!</b></font>

232
00:20:43,984 --> 00:20:46,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are you, scared?!</b></font>

233
00:20:46,654 --> 00:20:48,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're useless!</b></font>

234
00:20:48,824 --> 00:20:51,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're nothing but dead weight.</b></font>

235
00:20:51,694 --> 00:20:53,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Dead weight?!
--You're freight,</b></font>

236
00:20:53,624 --> 00:20:56,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>messing up the power-to-weight ratio!</b></font>

237
00:20:56,494 --> 00:20:58,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>She gets tough behind the wheel!</i></b></font>

238
00:20:58,504 --> 00:21:00,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not freight!</b></font>

239
00:21:00,864 --> 00:21:04,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not fat! I have a nice body!</b></font>

240
00:21:04,174 --> 00:21:06,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Forty-nine kilograms of extra weight!</b></font>

241
00:21:06,644 --> 00:21:09,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I weigh 47!</b></font>

242
00:21:10,444 --> 00:21:13,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Fine, I've got my pride, too!</b></font>

243
00:21:15,684 --> 00:21:17,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ready, Mako?</b></font>

244
00:21:17,554 --> 00:21:19,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll put our lives on the line!</b></font>

245
00:21:19,554 --> 00:21:21,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Welcome back!</b></font>

246
00:21:21,454 --> 00:21:26,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>All right. Enter the next turn so
you almost scrape the inside wall!</b></font>

247
00:21:26,224 --> 00:21:28,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Got it!</b></font>

248
00:21:45,914 --> 00:21:47,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Not bad.</i></b></font>

249
00:21:49,684 --> 00:21:53,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I improved while recklessly chasing her.</i></b></font>

250
00:21:58,424 --> 00:22:01,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I can feel the rhythm now!</i></b></font>

251
00:22:01,164 --> 00:22:03,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm synched in!</i></b></font>

252
00:22:04,664 --> 00:22:07,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Not many corners left now...</i></b></font>

253
00:22:07,504 --> 00:22:12,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll just have to attack</i>
<i>each corner as well as I can!</i></b></font>

254
00:22:12,244 --> 00:22:14,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I want no regrets.</i></b></font>

255
00:22:14,574 --> 00:22:18,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride as Usui's fastest is on the line.</i></b></font>

256
00:22:34,524 --> 00:22:40,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai ni tsukare hate samayotteta koro</i></b></font>

257
00:22:40,364 --> 00:22:48,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yokubou dake ni kararete miushinatteita</i></b></font>

258
00:22:48,214 --> 00:22:54,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kimagure na unmei wa</i></b></font>

259
00:22:54,614 --> 00:23:02,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mujaki na hitomi ni miserarete yuku</i></b></font>

260
00:23:03,624 --> 00:23:10,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sake bara no you ni akaku</i>
<i>tsuyoku, tsuyoku kimi o daite</i></b></font>

261
00:23:10,164 --> 00:23:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tatta hitotsu kono omoi o shinjitsu da to ieru</i></b></font>

262
00:23:16,974 --> 00:23:22,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yorokobi o kanadeyou...</i></b></font>

263
00:23:22,144 --> 00:23:29,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kagayaku mirai e</i></b></font>

264
00:23:41,194 --> 00:23:48,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kazoe kirenai hodo tashikame aou</i></b></font>

265
00:23:48,874 --> 00:23:54,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Jounetsu yo eien e todoke</i></b></font>

266
00:23:54,944 --> 00:24:01,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sake bara no you ni akaku</i>
<i>tsuyoku, tsuyoku dakishimete</i></b></font>

267
00:24:01,614 --> 00:24:08,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Tatoe nani o ushinattemo</i>
<i>kono ude o hanasanai</i></b></font>

268
00:24:08,454 --> 00:24:13,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Utsukushiku karen ni sake...</i></b></font>

269
00:24:13,694 --> 00:24:20,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kiseki no hana yo</i></b></font>

270
00:24:26,544 --> 00:24:30,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Bunta, do you think Takumi has</i>
<i>a chance against the Sileighty?</i></b></font>

271
00:24:30,514 --> 00:24:32,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--Who knows?</i>
<i>--Who knows?!</i></b></font>

272
00:24:32,514 --> 00:24:35,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I sell tofu, not predictions.</i></b></font>

273
00:24:35,654 --> 00:24:39,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--I'll have Gunmo and Atsuage.</i>
<i>--I have seasoned that Eight-Six.</i></b></font>

274
00:24:39,184 --> 00:24:41,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>No one can touch it downhill.</i></b></font>

275
00:24:41,724 --> 00:24:43,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It's up to the driver.</i></b></font>

276
00:24:43,494 --> 00:24:45,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>We'll see next week.</i></b></font>

277
00:24:45,594 --> 00:24:48,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What if I bought Momen and Kinugoshi, too?</i></b></font>

278
00:24:48,334 --> 00:24:51,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next on Initial D: "Super Drift."</i></b></font>

279
00:24:51,334 --> 00:24:54,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--It's a must-see.</i>
<i>--Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

